column16: Lighting was subpar. Enjoyed the performance.

We enjoyed the very talented musicians very much! Went to both performances. P&Wolf they were SO amazing not only playing together but also acting!! Thank you for bringing them to (America) Walla Walla.

column17: I have no suggstions except "keep up the good work"

column16:
The Power House is the perfect venue for a concert like this. All seats are wonderful! Sound: wonderful! Lights: wonderful!
We love coming a bit early to get parking and a glass of wine before the show. It makes the evening extra special. The ushers, greeters and wine servers were all so friendly and helpful!
column17: I would encourage you to maintain the high level of professional, family-friendly, and noncontroversial entertainment selections. Several of your recent/current performers are very offensive.
